by one rectangle.

00:53:53.870 --> 00:53:56.920
So that general pattern--

00:53:56.920 --> 00:54:00.110
those are what I've found are
the most useful ways of

00:54:00.110 --> 00:54:01.340
dealing with complex problems.

00:54:01.340 --> 00:54:08.430
So these are the big ideas
in that course.

