Whenever you go to
a new field--

01:00:49.610 --> 01:00:51.490
so there's a Nobel
Prize winner at

01:00:51.490 --> 01:00:53.390
Harvard, Walter Gilbert.

01:00:53.390 --> 01:00:55.700
So he's worked in I think
chemistry, physics, and

01:00:55.700 --> 01:00:57.410
biology, many different
fields.

