You could look at scientific
writing.

01:02:25.150 --> 01:02:27.090
You could look at writing
scientific papers.

01:02:27.090 --> 01:02:29.780
You can look at giving
presentations.

01:02:29.780 --> 01:02:32.200
Doing it on problem sets so they
communicate, you can have

01:02:32.200 --> 01:02:34.330
students exchange problem
sets with each other.

01:02:34.330 --> 01:02:36.430
If they can't understand the
other problem set, clearly it

01:02:36.430 --> 01:02:38.960
